Titolo: Warriors Orochi 4

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Warriors Orochi 4, released as Musou Orochi 3 (無双OROCHI 3, Musō Orochi Surī) in Japan, is a 2018 hack and slash video game developed by Koei Tecmo and Omega Force for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch. First announced in March 2018, it is the fifth installment of the crossover series Warriors Orochi, a combination of the Dynasty Warriors and Samurai Warriors series. The game was released in Japan on September 27, 2018, in North America on October 16, 2018, and in Europe on October 19, 2018.An updated version, titled Warriors Orochi 4 Ultimate (known in Japan as Musou Orochi 3 Ultimate (無双OROCHI 3, Musō Orochi Surī Ultimate)), was released in Japan on December 19, 2019, and was released in North America and Europe on February 14, 2020.

Genere: Hack and slash

Valutazione: 69
